{"tid":1844923,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"請珍惜Kobe...（認真）","createTime":"2020-01-27T00:33:00.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-01T16:05:40.000Z","uid":64576,"like":22,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"ddd4023fb4f01c7701729af55447e08e0b1308c1","tid":1844923,"uid":64576,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-27T00:33:00.000Z","msg":"細個開始睇波果陣好拎憎Utah Jazz，覺得Stockton、Hornacek、Malone好拎茅（當年Playoff Malone一?批暈Robinson），次次進攻都好似教科書一?既戰術好悶<br />\n<br />\n到佢地退晒休，先知果D老練既技術／走位係好野黎<br />\n<br />\nPenny既獨特節奏、Grant Hill（全盛時期）既First Step、Reggie Miller對贏波既執著，都係到退休／收左皮先發現佢地原來咁拎勁<br />\n<br />\n高登仔好多人都反Kobe，但係老實講佢既Foot Work技術、Clutch Shots能力、對比賽既執著，冇人比得上佢（我覺得依家LeBron&gt;&gt;Kobe）<br />\n<br />\n我諗Kobe最多都係打多1、2年就退休，其實睇得1場得1場，好好珍惜<br />\n<br />\n利申：Webber年代Kings迷<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />rip"},{"pid":"86baa37b9319da3fa7a95160932a79dad8ba9134","tid":1844923,"uid":85327,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-27T00:34:45.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"343c5079b4419524d6b781a38d580b383d01c762","tid":1844923,"uid":149494,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-27T00:46:59.000Z","msg":"同樓主同一時代開始睇波<br />\nKobe初初入聯盟嗰陣真係好憎佢<br />\n覺得佢只係山寨MJ<br />\n連penny, hill等等都遠遠比不上<br />\n一憎憎咗廿幾年"},{"pid":"f32bff5980df28b16d775dcdda6e4b863125b07a","tid":1844923,"uid":280469,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-27T00:52:59.000Z","msg":"footwork無乜邊個真係好得過kobe<br />\nlbj只係體能上令你覺得好過kobe, 但細膩度kobe真係無得彈<br />\n利申小牛迷，11年比牛橫掃固然心涼，但見odom bynum artest都打茅波時，得佢一個默默撐起隊波就覺得佢係一等一true star"},{"pid":"3e83102b9a2d19e8f147089e21ffa9e35b839da6","tid":1844923,"uid":228143,"like":1,"dislike":8,"score":-7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-27T00:57:44.000Z","msg":"Clutch Shots<br />\n<br />\n應該ray allen最強啦<br />\n<br />\n高比後期回晒塘啦<br />\n<br />\n有冇人真心討論<br />\n<br />\n佢都係靠oneal<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />好彩起大城市 勁多強隊友"},{"pid":"d5289ff148fca1f11b35eade8109294e488784f2","tid":1844923,"uid":228143,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-27T00:59:02.000Z","msg":"高比係一個個人能力強<br />\n<br />\n唔識協調<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nwade比佢好好多  <br />\n<br />\n2個都經典"},{"pid":"f0991d914fc99c1b61871131674b29948342d67c","tid":1844923,"uid":10121,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"3e83102b9a2d19e8f147089e21ffa9e35b839da6","tid":1844923,"uid":228143,"like":1,"dislike":8,"score":-7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-27T00:57:44.000Z","msg":"Clutch Shots<br />\n<br />\n應該ray allen最強啦<br />\n<br />\n高比後期回晒塘啦<br />\n<br />\n有冇人真心討論<br />\n<br />\n佢都係靠oneal<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />好彩起大城市 勁多強隊友"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-27T01:00:00.000Z","msg":"邊有人有心情同你今日討論<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"09be29f88ec90ed7bad3b4b0564f71b5b1d9ce63","tid":1844923,"uid":129087,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-27T01:00:37.000Z","msg":"又撚新會員"},{"pid":"f6eaeca525a08a02f2f788026642e180809d00b1","tid":1844923,"uid":228143,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"f0991d914fc99c1b61871131674b29948342d67c","tid":1844923,"uid":10121,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"3e83102b9a2d19e8f147089e21ffa9e35b839da6","tid":1844923,"uid":228143,"like":1,"dislike":8,"score":-7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-27T00:57:44.000Z","msg":"Clutch Shots<br />\n<br />\n應該ray allen最強啦<br />\n<br />\n高比後期回晒塘啦<br />\n<br />\n有冇人真心討論<br />\n<br />\n佢都係靠oneal<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\"